div.p:
I deſire exceedingly to rejoyce in the beholding your Order, and the ſtedfaſtneſs of your faith in Chriſt: for I much fear leſt by ſome means the Tempter ſhould tempt you, or ſome of you, and ſo my labour be ſo far in vain, as the temptation doth prevail: And ſome of you may remember, I forewarned you of this hour of temptation long before; which I told you would try the ſtrongeſt Chriſtians, ſo reputed; but now plainly ſee, if Ancient Profeſſors among you be not very circumſpect, you may ſee that Scripture further fulfilled every day; 

                     •
                  he firſt ſhall be last, and the laſt ſhall be firſt.
